# Sensec OCR
This project runs OCR on the /files directory and saves the results in 
a Postgres database


##### Table of Contents  
[Requirements](#Requirements)  
[Installation](#Installation)  


## Requirements
Requirements
At a minimum, the user must have pip and Docker installed. 

## Installation
Installation

The package requirements are included in the requirements.txt. To install the required packages
on your local directory, execute the following command:

`pip3 install -r requirements.txt` 

To run the directory, first modify the `docker-compose-ankura.yml` file's volume mapping section to pull in the local file directory 
to be mapped the Docker image, as seen in the example below:

`volumes:
      - /path/to/filedirectory:/files
`
